{
  "texts": [
    "Despite the high performance of the developed sensing procedure, there are some features that could be improved with further iterations of the SERS sensor, NN and analytical setup.",
    "They are: (1) the micropore size of the Ag foam used in this work determines the maximum size of MPs -262 µm.",
    "However, macroporous templates with larger pore sizes or more complex networks could be generated using additive manufacturing 58.",
    "And much larger MPs are commonly determined by visual methods 59, 60.",
    "(2) Ag does not have an indefinite shelflife."
  ]
}